# Complete Login Flow
# Demonstrates form interaction and authentication

# Click login button
CLICK `#login-btn`

# Wait for login modal
WAIT `.login-form` 3

# Fill in credentials
CLICK `#email`
TYPE "demo@example.com"

CLICK `#password`
TYPE "demo123"

# Check remember me
IF (EXISTS `#remember-me`) THEN CLICK `#remember-me`

# Submit form
CLICK `button[type="submit"]`

# Wait for success
WAIT `.welcome-message` 5

# Verify login succeeded
IF (EXISTS `.user-info`) THEN EVAL `console.log('âœ… Login successful!')`